{"tid":1238944,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"波子718 Cayman / Boxster引頸以待的終極車型登場","createTime":"2019-06-18T04:01:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T21:31:26.000Z","uid":236926,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"5775150cee95cc62fd04955e407cf2db243b0e01","tid":1238944,"uid":236926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:01:18.000Z","msg":"睇標題大家都估到係GT4啦~<br />\n之前傳聞又話會用四缸又話會用六缸<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/c5F9Bthu-yQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fc5F9Bthu-yQ&d=7EcP4%2BvGpl6inSsjOqiUXiHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=985f02b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/c5F9Bthu-yQ</a><br />\n<br />\n究竟除左外型同上一代有咩唔同呢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OQs0bDs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOQs0bDs.jpg&h=99821106&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/HsXTYbjC5DI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHsXTYbjC5DI&d=7EcP4%2BvGpl6inSsjOqiUXiHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=dd0661b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/HsXTYbjC5DI</a><br />\n今次718 Cayman GT4 同 718 Spyder共同推出<br />\n<br />\n今代Spyder不再只係部輕量化Boxster，而可視為GT4的開蓬版<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xQcfK7m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxQcfK7m.jpg&h=d8ddf1fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">*上代2011的Boxster Spyder</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ow4BuCQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOw4BuCQ.jpg&h=72eca210&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩部新車並未如傳聞所講用detune的991 GT3引擎，而是共用一副度身定造的4公升水平對向6氣缸自然吸氣引擎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CC0MRJX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCC0MRJX.jpg&h=114acee4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JfjYHTK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJfjYHTK.jpg&h=7f94726c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n馬力為420匹，比上代多出35匹<br />\n最高轉速達7600rpm，峰值扭力在5000-6800rpm輸出<br />\n<br />\n該引擎反而是基於991 / 992 Carrera，有20％的結構是相同，並與其共享生產線製作<br />\n<br />\n0-100km/h 加速只需4.4秒<br />\n718 CaymanGT4最高速可達304km/h(188mph)<br />\n而718 Spyder則可達301km/h(187mph)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n與傳聞不同，新車暫時只有六速手動波箱，並未有PDK波箱選項<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/soWDHRF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsoWDHRF.jpg&h=fa7a110d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sEeRip1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsEeRip1.jpg&h=6707c08f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n保時捷的GT街車部門主管Andreas Preuninger表示，雖然曾經有考慮使用PDK，但棍波為GT4本身其中－項的重要原素，所以繼續沿用<br />\n<br />\n車身比普通718矮30mm<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hxe57iy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHxe57iy.jpg&h=e7952ab5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n受惠於Spyder版需要更多的下壓力，新車比上代GT4的下壓多50％<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/51jRiqd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F51jRiqd.jpg&h=dc181c4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7KJywDt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7KJywDt.jpg&h=212b14c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但重量為1420kg，比上代多30kg<br />\n因為使用了更大的電池，新增start stop功能，及死氣喉的粒子過濾裝置，以符合環保要求<br />\n<br />\n制動性能上，剎車標準配置aluminium monobloc fixed-calliper brakes，車主可選配效率更高的 Porsche Ceramic Composite Brake (PCCB) <br />\n車胎兩部車都使用米芝蓮的Pilot Sport Cup 2，前245/35 ZR20, 後295/30 ZR20<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fvQ85jy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfvQ85jy.jpg&h=fa4fa7d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6FhO5jz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6FhO5jz.jpg&h=0a2bcd6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n賽道表現方面，在Nurburing Nordschleife的圈速比上代GT4快10秒，能達與991 GT3睇齊的7分12秒範圍<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eqoFV49.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeqoFV49.jpg&h=03ccffcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">*991 GT3</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XjcGFO3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXjcGFO3.jpg&h=4c328030&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果GT4的買家想更加熱血，更可選配Clubsport裝備，該選項會加裝防滾架，賽車座椅，司機六點式安全帶及滅火筒，以供更極烈駕駛之用<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ioPef8F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FioPef8F.jpg&h=e5ac763b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Orp57op.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOrp57op.jpg&h=40e91e1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NgszggL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNgszggL.jpg&h=964eb71a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n車價方面，GT4為&pound;75,348，Spyder版較平，為&pound;73,405<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.netcarshow.com/porsche/2020-718_cayman_gt4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.netcarshow.com%2Fporsche%2F2020-718_cayman_gt4%2F&d=7EcP4%2BvGpl6inSsjOqiUXiHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=45473cd3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.netcarshow.com/porsche/2020-718_cayman_gt4/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.netcarshow.com/porsche/2020-718_spyder/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.netcarshow.com%2Fporsche%2F2020-718_spyder%2F&d=7EcP4%2BvGpl6inSsjOqiUXiHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=cd97baab\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.netcarshow.com/porsche/2020-718_spyder/</a>"},{"pid":"5be7c84f2cdac20ec97831c6b84f2977a09eb09a","tid":1238944,"uid":247934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:13:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 